<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.5">
<l>poṅku pōtiyum piṇṭi yumuṭaip puttar nōṉpiyar paḷḷi yuḷḷuṟai</l>
<l>taṅkaḷ tēvarun tāṅka ḷumē  yākaveṉ neñcamaṉpāy</l>
<l>eṅkum vāṉavar tāṉa varniṟain tēttum vēṅkaṭam mēvi niṉṟaruḷ</l>
<l>aṅka ṇāyakaṟ kiṉṟa ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My companion heart, today you assumed the duty of service to the lord</l>
<l rend="indent">with beautiful eyes who is gracious,</l>
<l>Always dwelling at Vēṅkaṭam where celestials and Dānavas,</l>
<l rend="indent">abounding everywhere, praise [him],</l>
<l>Since he even is the gods which abide in the shrines</l>
<l rend="indent">with flourishing bodhi and aśoka [trees]</l>
<l>Of the Buddhists and [Jain] ascetic, and is [them] also.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
